title: Lies & Arbor Gold (w/Chloe Ketchum)
description:
We were joined by Chloe of Girls Gone Canon & Drunk ASOIAF History to discuss a recurring theme of deception. Sansa, Young Griff, Cersei, Wyman Manderly, Varys and plenty more. Published July 30, 2020.

PS there's a bit of scratchiness in the audio on this one, our apologies.

Girls Gone Canon: https://girlsgonecanon.podbean.com/
Drunk ASOIAF History: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCr3MDu4CPVPFDa5DvvwFufQ
